________________________________________
5️⃣ Understanding Each Section
resources
resources:
- database
- exoplanets
This tells Kustomize to include:
base/database
base/exoplanets
Each contains Kubernetes YAML manifests.
________________________________________
secretGenerator
secretGenerator:
- name: db-secrets
Creates a Kubernetes Secret automatically.
Stored values:
DB_ADMIN_PASSWORD
DB_NAME
DB_PASSWORD
DB_USER
This secret is used by the database deployment.
________________________________________
configMapGenerator
configMapGenerator:
- name: db-config
Creates a ConfigMap with:
DB_HOST
DB_PORT
Used by the exoplanets application.
________________________________________
Important Behavior: Hash Suffix
Kustomize adds a hash to generated resources.
Example:
db-config-2d7thbcgkc
db-secrets-55cbgc8c6m
Why?
If values change → hash changes → pods redeploy.
This ensures configuration updates trigger rolling updates automatically.
