1️⃣2️⃣ Production Overlay (v1.1.3)
Switch branch:
git checkout v1.1.3
New directory appears:
overlays/production
________________________________________
Overlay Structure
overlays/production
 ├ kustomization.yaml
 └ patch-replicas.yaml
________________________________________
Overlay kustomization.yaml
kind: Kustomization
resources:
- ../../base/

patches:
- path: patch-replicas.yaml
  target:
    kind: Deployment
    name: exoplanets
Meaning:
Use base resources but apply a patch.
________________________________________
Patch File
patch-replicas.yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: exoplanets
spec:
  replicas: 2
Effect:
replicas: 1
→
replicas: 2
________________________________________
Deploy Production Overlay
Command
oc apply -k overlays/production
Now OpenShift updates deployment.
________________________________________
Check Replicas
Command
oc get deployment
Output
deployment/exoplanets 2/2
Two pods running.
